channel.title: @ECONOMY RESET@@Help@
channel.description:
I'm currently having some issues with my economy reset. I just want to delete all items in inventory, and in bank, but leave their stats alone. I keep making my own .bat and .java files to do reset for economy but it is not working. I'm currently running off the source: Project Dungeonfest, or Mezzyscape. It is a 562/659, if you could help me out I would be greatly appreciated.
QUESTION: HOW CAN I MAKE A ECONOMY RESET .BAT AND HOW DO I DO IT?

item.title: @ECONOMY RESET@@Help@
item.dc:creator: @Camballer Camballer
item.description:
@Camballer wrote:

@echo off
Title Economy Manager
“C:/Program Files (x86)/Java/jdk1.6.0_25/bin/java” -cp bin EcoManager
pause
